<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="240" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,896,1175]" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,968,994]" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">Remarks:</emphasis>
When proposed this species, 
<bibRefCitation author="Chopard, L." box="[651,887,968,995]" pageId="13" pageNumber="240" pagination="273 - 290" refId="ref13806" refString="Chopard, L. (1968) Beitrage zur kenntnis der fauna Afghanistans, Gryllodea et Tridactyloidea. Casopis Moravskeho Musea Acta Musei Moraviae, 53, 273 - 290." type="journal article" year="1968">Chopard (1968: 276)</bibRefCitation>
indicated that it is difficult to distinguish it from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1804" box="[151,336,1004,1031]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Gryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bordigalensis">
<emphasis box="[151,168,1005,1030]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">E</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[185,336,1004,1030]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">bordigalensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(= 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Latreille" baseAuthorityYear="1804" box="[371,522,1004,1030]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Tartarogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="burdigalensis">
<emphasis box="[371,522,1004,1030]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">burdigalensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) unless using male’s genitalia to identify them. When established the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority=", Gorochov (1986)" authorityName=", Gorochov" authorityYear="1986" box="[151,552,1040,1067]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Eumodicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,342,1040,1066]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">Eumodicogryllus</emphasis>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[358,552,1040,1067]" pageId="13" pageNumber="240" pagination="3 - 15" refId="ref14109" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (1986) New and little known Grylloidea (Orthoptera) from Middle Asia and adjacent territories. Proceedings of Zoological Institute of Academy of Sciences of USSR, 140, 3 - 15." type="journal article" year="1986">Gorochov (1986)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
arranged this species in the taxon, but it is not included in the elevated genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName=", Gorochov" authorityYear="1986" box="[151,342,1076,1102]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Eumodicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,342,1076,1102]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">Eumodicogryllus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
now (Cigliano, 
<emphasis box="[527,584,1076,1102]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">et al.</emphasis>
, 2021). According to features of its epiphallus (referring to 
<bibRefCitation author="Chopard, L." pageId="13" pageNumber="240" pagination="273 - 290" refId="ref13806" refString="Chopard, L. (1968) Beitrage zur kenntnis der fauna Afghanistans, Gryllodea et Tridactyloidea. Casopis Moravskeho Musea Acta Musei Moraviae, 53, 273 - 290." type="journal article" year="1968">Chopard, 1968: 275</bibRefCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[207,270,1112,1138]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1452,1476]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,179,1426]" captionTargetId="figure-18@3.[151,1436,179,1426]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Ovipositor of Modicogryllini and regarding species. A–D. inside of ovipositor; E–H. outside of ovipositor. A and E. T. rufoniger; B and F. M. (P.) consobrinus; C and G. S. siamensis; D and H. E. chinensis comb. nov." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5026196" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5026196/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
), this species should be placed in 
<taxonomicName authorityName=", Gorochov" authorityYear="1986" box="[649,840,1112,1138]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Eumodicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[649,840,1112,1138]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">Eumodicogryllus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as done by 
<bibRefCitation author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[972,1165,1112,1139]" pageId="13" pageNumber="240" pagination="3 - 15" refId="ref14109" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (1986) New and little known Grylloidea (Orthoptera) from Middle Asia and adjacent territories. Proceedings of Zoological Institute of Academy of Sciences of USSR, 140, 3 - 15." type="journal article" year="1986">Gorochov (1986)</bibRefCitation>
because it does not possess the characters of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Tarbinsky" authorityYear="1940" box="[395,556,1148,1174]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Tartarogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[395,556,1148,1174]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="240">Tartarogryllus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
